            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Gurgius">Gurgio</name></persName> filio bone
                        memorie <persName><name ref="Bonitius">Bonitii</name></persName> vende a
                            <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Leo">Leo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> filio bone memorie <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Iohannis</name></persName> (…) una <rs key="#Petiae"
                            >petia</rs> de terra mea illa quam in loco et finibus <placeName
                            key="#Churches" ref="#places/87">prope <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                            <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/127">Sancti
                                Iusti</orgName></placeName>, quod uno capo tenet in <orgName
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/127">beati
                            Sancti Iusti</orgName>, et alio capo tenet in terra <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Priests #Consortes/shared_possessions"><name
                                ref="Ghisulfus">Ghisolfi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiteri</rs> et de <rs
                            key="#Consortes/shared_possessions">consortibus</rs> suis, lato uno
                        tenet in terra <persName key="#Confinia #Petiae"><name ref="Winigis"
                                >Winigi</name></persName> et alio lato tenet in terra <orgName
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/86"
                            >Sacti Cerboni</orgName>, con tutte le sue dipendenze, per il prezzo di
                        argentum sol. vihinti in prefinito. Chiede a <orgName key="#Writer #Notary"
                                ><name ref="Brunicardus">Brondicardi</name></orgName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notari</rs> domini imperatoris la stesura della cartula.
                        Actum loco <placeName ref="#places/265">Massa</placeName>. Testimoni:
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Contulinus"
                            >Guntolini</name></persName> filio bone memorie <persName><name
                                ref="Mantius">Mainti</name></persName>; <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Teutius">Teuti</name></persName> filio bone memorie
                                <persName><name ref="Suavitius">Suaviti</name></persName>; <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Eribaldus">Eribaldi</name></persName> filio
                        bone memorie <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName>. Scrive:
                        Brondicardo notarius domni imperatoris.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
